This template is used to mark pages for deletion, categorizing them in [[:Category:Candidates for deletion]].

==Usage==

Type <code><nowiki>{{delete}}</nowiki></code> on the page to be deleted.

===Extra parameters===

====proposed====
For a contact link, e.g. <code><nowiki>{{delete|proposed=[[Message_Wall:User|User]]}}</nowiki></code>.

====reason====
To provide a specific reason for deletion, e.g. <code><nowiki>{{delete|proposed=[[Message_Wall:User|User]]|reason=Author request}}</nowiki></code> or <code><nowiki>{{delete|Reason here}}</nowiki></code>.

